name: DOS X TRIP
description:
This guy took too much weed for this friday night, can you feel that?

// Interactive piece - move your mouse and click to make things trippy //

This piece is a special tribute to one of the biggest names in HEN @maxcapacity, and his wonderful collection (turned into a real family) DOS PUNKS! Being a part of this has been amazing, and this is a little tribute of thanks for your art and person. Is also my piece for celebrating HEN500K, it's being a beautiful journey with you all, thank you so much for changing my life forever!

This piece was created based on my studies with Hydra Synth through a  generative code in HTML with modified functions.
>> https://hydra.ojack.xyz/ <<

by @temenosart
